Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How enjoyable! How truly enjoyable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the extent of my power!\NNot by a long shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you haven't forgotten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Antirrhinum majus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri Shinmei Style,\NIntermediate Skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Six Slaying Wasps!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.78,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clinching Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The figures for this rate\Nof increase are insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stop him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But RM-C's already ceded Limit Control,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so there's nothing I can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can still force-quit, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The puppet's central system\Ncould sustain some damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what should\Nbe done if necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, it might not be so obvious,\Nbut I really do have faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in them, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should've realized it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how ironclad\Nthat protective wall may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it can't possibly trade blows\Nhead-on with the Ser=Versta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing\Nthat was able to do that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Gravi-Sheath, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unless it's another Ogre Lux,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it shouldn't be able to block\Nthe Ser=Versta's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AR-D must be using\NUlm Manadite as his engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that was AR-D\Nrampaging out of control right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, though I'm sure all that\Npower's more than he can manage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,most likely AR-D is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it! This is my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder my master\Nwarned me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has it under control?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, I hate to see this end,\Nbut what do you say we settle this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out, Rafflesia!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, it's my turn to pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... you will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, why don't we\Npick up where we left off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least I'd like to say so,\Nbut maybe not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could eclipse his speed,\Nthen I could strike a decisive blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speed, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I remember Claudia telling me once
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that the Ser=Versta is known to assume\Nthe form that best suits its wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we can make it do that, wouldn't that\Ngive us some chance of winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm not good at making\Nminor tweaks to my Prana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me handle that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is pour\Nyour Prana into this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, try to picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ideal Ser=Versta\Nthat you can wield most comfortably
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in terms of shape and size!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato Amagiri's Ser=Versta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the ideal form for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is all that I can do in this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the rest to you, Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, as it happens,\NI was a bit out of shape myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I'm going to end this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This match is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style\NHidden Technique...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Moon of Carnage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}AMAGIRI SHINMEI STYLE\NHIDDEN TECHNIQUE\NMOON OF CARNAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ernesta Kuhne... Badge broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Winners, Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been trounced!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-At last! At last, it's over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After a showdown of epic proportions,\Nthe Phoenix Festa has been won by...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seidoukan Academy's Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two-week-long Phoenix Festa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, we've seen\Nnumerous epic battles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we were particularly astonished\Nby AR-D and RM-C's fighting skills, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the team that prevailed against\Nthem in that slugfest of a final was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seidoukan Academy's\NAmagiri/Riessfield team!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, offering his\Ncongratulations to Ayato Amagiri{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is the Steering Committee chairman,\NMr. Madiath Mesa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I commend you both\Nfor your brilliant triumph,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your unbreakable spirit\Nand this glorious victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found your matches\Nextremely compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to seeing\Nwhat you'll accomplish in the next festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ladies and gentlemen, please give\NMr. Amagiri a warm round of applause!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, everybody, see you again\Nnext time, at the Gryps Festa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Festa commentary was brought to you\Nby yours truly, Meeko Yanase and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your analyst, Pham Thi Tram!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grimalkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Eye... Number 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Verner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That scar on your cheek...\NI know it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Shadow Star shinobi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You... Whose orders\Nare you carrying out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a truly magnificent match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I owe it all to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, Yabuki and MacPhail\Nall pitched in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lester?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's nothing to thank me for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Yabuki blackmailed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I had no choice\Nbut to help out. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Lester. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come to think of it,\Nwhere is Yabuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard bounced\Nin the middle of the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragging me out there,\Nthen ditching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see him,\Nhe's gonna wish he was never born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a Transformation Spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was brand-new, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sorry, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't capture the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you all got out of there safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Lester?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just say, "Congrats."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lester?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That MacPhail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He just can't show\Nhis honest feelings, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we help...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya Sasamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for a rematch with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see why. We lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During yesterday's semifinal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you and Dr. Sasamiya's Lux\Nwas clearly superior to RM-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But not enough to beat the fused AR-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Using the fused AR-D is virtually\Nthe same as using an Ogre Lux.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ferrovius's philosophies are incompatible\Nwith anything as unstable as an Ogre Lux.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I personally cannot\Nacknowledge that as a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. Let's duel again\Nand settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'm going to pummel you\Nuntil there's nothing left
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and finish you off once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nwe'll have to be better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:16:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why don't you give me\Nyour answer from the other day?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether or not\Nyou're going to join forces with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that! Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, my answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just aren't my cup of tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are you sure you're really going to\Nbe able to finish the third puppet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't find any compatible\NUlm Manadite, can you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I see. Hats off to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't even\Ntold Camilla about her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you'd expect of Rewolf, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can at least\Nlisten to what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fine. I'll be in touch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All righty, who knows\Nwhat's going to happen next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your victory,\NAyato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was only able to win\Nbecause you guys did such a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh no, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are the police done questioning you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gave them an earful about\Nwhat a heinous guy Dirk Eberwein is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know I caused you all\Nso much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault\Nthat it happened, Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it was such an important match\Nfor you and the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And to make matters worse,\NLady Toudou got these terrible injuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's high time you let it go, Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good kid,\Nbut you're still only ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to cry when you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were so brave, Flora.\NYou're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, I did summon you here\Nbecause I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when push comes to shove...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it, but you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I stained your\Nprecious handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'd challenge me to another duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't teamed up with you,\NI couldn't have gotten this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,\Nmy wish came true, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd come\Nthis far either... not without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is merely one checkpoint for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join you for the ride.\NFor you and for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's start with a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate today's victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hoping for our next victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The perpetrators have been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The abduction was carried out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by a mafia gang running the casino\Nwhere Ms. Klem was held captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!\NThat was clearly the work of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't been able\Nto find a shred of evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,linking the Dante Ms. Sasamiya and\NMs. Toudou fought to any specific academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the investigation\Nwill continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd like you to take\Na more long-term view of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- By the way, Amagiri...\N- Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that as the winner\Nof the Phoenix Festa,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you've requested a search\Nfor your older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she went missing here in Asterisk,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there must be\Nsome clues left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be praying for her safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, thanks to you,\NI'm completely swamped!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only did it out of concern for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, your methods\Nwere too violent this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I wish\Nyou'd try to hold back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}aren't you going to tell him about\Nyour relationship with that woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I have\Nno intention of going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's a private matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what am I going to do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's strange. For some reason,\NI'm recalling a scandal...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, but there's nothing\Nwe can do about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Julis, my Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Congratulations on winning\Nthe Phoenix Festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 22\NLieseltania
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's just zip through the next one, too!
